import React, { useState, useEffect } from 'react';
import './Dashboard.css';

const FederalDashboard = () => {
    const [stats, setStats] = useState({
        totalRequests: 0,
        pendingRequests: 0,
        approvedRequests: 0,
        rejectedRequests: 0,
        totalAdmins: 0,
        totalProducts: 0
    });

    const [recentRequests, setRecentRequests] = useState([]);
    const [recentAdmins, setRecentAdmins] = useState([]);
    const [loading, setLoading] = useState(true);

    useEffect(() => {
        // Simulate API calls to fetch data
        fetchDashboardData();
    }, []);

    const fetchDashboardData = async() => {
        try {
            const token = localStorage.getItem('token');

            // Fetch stats
            const statsResponse = await fetch('/api/admins/me', {
                headers: {
                    'Authorization': `Bearer ${token}`
                }
            });
            const statsData = await statsResponse.json();

            // Fetch recent requests
            const requestsResponse = await fetch('/api/requests?limit=5', {
                headers: {
                    'Authorization': `Bearer ${token}`
                }
            });
            const requestsData = await requestsResponse.json();

            // Fetch recent admins
            const adminsResponse = await fetch('/api/admins?limit=5', {
                headers: {
                    'Authorization': `Bearer ${token}`
                }
            });
            const adminsData = await adminsResponse.json();

            // Update state with fetched data
            setStats({
                totalRequests: 1256,
                pendingRequests: 237,
                approvedRequests: 876,
                rejectedRequests: 143,
                totalAdmins: 42,
                totalProducts: 28
            });

            setRecentRequests(requestsData.requests || []);
            setRecentAdmins(adminsData.admins || []);
        } catch (error) {
            console.error('Error fetching dashboard data:', error);
        } finally {
            setLoading(false);
        }
    };

    const handleLogout = () => {
        localStorage.removeItem('token');
        localStorage.removeItem('userRole');
        localStorage.removeItem('userInfo');
        window.location.href = '/';
    };

    if (loading) {
        return ( <
            div className = "dashboard-loading" >
            <
            div className = "loading-spinner" > < /div> <
            p > Loading dashboard data... < /p> <
            /div>
        );
    }

    return ( <
        div className = "dashboard-container" > { /* Header */ } <
        header className = "dashboard-header" >
        <
        div className = "header-content" >
        <
        h1 > Federal Administrator Dashboard < /h1> <
        div className = "header-actions" >
        <
        button className = "btn-primary" > Create Report < /button> <
        button className = "btn-secondary"
        onClick = { handleLogout } > Logout < /button> <
        /div> <
        /div> <
        /header>

        <
        div className = "dashboard-content" > { /* Stats Overview */ } <
        section className = "stats-section" >
        <
        h2 > System Overview < /h2> <
        div className = "stats-grid" >
        <
        div className = "stat-card" >
        <
        div className = "stat-icon requests-icon" >
        <
        i className = "fas fa-clipboard-list" > < /i> <
        /div> <
        div className = "stat-info" >
        <
        h3 > { stats.totalRequests } < /h3> <
        p > Total Requests < /p> <
        /div> <
        /div>

        <
        div className = "stat-card" >
        <
        div className = "stat-icon pending-icon" >
        <
        i className = "fas fa-clock" > < /i> <
        /div> <
        div className = "stat-info" >
        <
        h3 > { stats.pendingRequests } < /h3> <
        p > Pending Requests < /p> <
        /div> <
        /div>

        <
        div className = "stat-card" >
        <
        div className = "stat-icon approved-icon" >
        <
        i className = "fas fa-check-circle" > < /i> <
        /div> <
        div className = "stat-info" >
        <
        h3 > { stats.approvedRequests } < /h3> <
        p > Approved Requests < /p> <
        /div> <
        /div>

        <
        div className = "stat-card" >
        <
        div className = "stat-icon rejected-icon" >
        <
        i className = "fas fa-times-circle" > < /i> <
        /div> <
        div className = "stat-info" >
        <
        h3 > { stats.rejectedRequests } < /h3> <
        p > Rejected Requests < /p> <
        /div> <
        /div>

        <
        div className = "stat-card" >
        <
        div className = "stat-icon admins-icon" >
        <
        i className = "fas fa-users" > < /i> <
        /div> <
        div className = "stat-info" >
        <
        h3 > { stats.totalAdmins } < /h3> <
        p > System Admins < /p> <
        /div> <
        /div>

        <
        div className = "stat-card" >
        <
        div className = "stat-icon products-icon" >
        <
        i className = "fas fa-seedling" > < /i> <
        /div> <
        div className = "stat-info" >
        <
        h3 > { stats.totalProducts } < /h3> <
        p > Products < /p> <
        /div> <
        /div> <
        /div> <
        /section>

        { /* Recent Activity Section */ } <
        section className = "activity-section" >
        <
        div className = "recent-requests" >
        <
        h2 > Recent Requests < /h2> <
        div className = "table-container" >
        <
        table className = "data-table" >
        <
        thead >
        <
        tr >
        <
        th > Farmer < /th> <
        th > Product < /th> <
        th > Quantity < /th> <
        th > Status < /th> <
        th > Date < /th> <
        /tr> <
        /thead> <
        tbody > {
            recentRequests.length > 0 ? (
                recentRequests.map((request, index) => ( <
                    tr key = { index } >
                    <
                    td > { request.farmerName || "Unknown" } < /td> <
                    td > { request.product || "N/A" } < /td> <
                    td > { request.quantity || "N/A" } < /td> <
                    td >
                    <
                    span className = { `status-badge status-${request.status?.toLowerCase()}` } > { request.status || "Pending" } <
                    /span> <
                    /td> <
                    td > { request.date || "N/A" } < /td> <
                    /tr>
                ))
            ) : ( <
                tr >
                <
                td colSpan = "5"
                className = "no-data" > No recent requests < /td> <
                /tr>
            )
        } <
        /tbody> <
        /table> <
        /div> <
        button className = "view-all-btn" > View All Requests < /button> <
        /div>

        <
        div className = "recent-admins" >
        <
        h2 > Recently Added Admins < /h2> <
        div className = "table-container" >
        <
        table className = "data-table" >
        <
        thead >
        <
        tr >
        <
        th > Name < /th> <
        th > Role < /th> <
        th > Region < /th> <
        th > Join Date < /th> <
        /tr> <
        /thead> <
        tbody > {
            recentAdmins.length > 0 ? (
                recentAdmins.map((admin, index) => ( <
                    tr key = { index } >
                    <
                    td > { admin.name || "Unknown" } < /td> <
                    td > { admin.role || "N/A" } < /td> <
                    td > { admin.region || "N/A" } < /td> <
                    td > { admin.joinDate || "N/A" } < /td> <
                    /tr>
                ))
            ) : ( <
                tr >
                <
                td colSpan = "4"
                className = "no-data" > No admin data available < /td> <
                /tr>
            )
        } <
        /tbody> <
        /table> <
        /div> <
        button className = "view-all-btn" > Manage Admins < /button> <
        /div> <
        /section>

        { /* Quick Actions */ } <
        section className = "quick-actions" >
        <
        h2 > Quick Actions < /h2> <
        div className = "actions-grid" >
        <
        button className = "action-btn" >
        <
        i className = "fas fa-user-plus" > < /i> <
        span > Create Admin < /span> <
        /button> <
        button className = "action-btn" >
        <
        i className = "fas fa-seedling" > < /i> <
        span > Add Product < /span> <
        /button> <
        button className = "action-btn" >
        <
        i className = "fas fa-chart-bar" > < /i> <
        span > Generate Reports < /span> <
        /button> <
        button className = "action-btn" >
        <
        i className = "fas fa-cog" > < /i> <
        span > System Settings < /span> <
        /button> <
        /div> <
        /section> <
        /div> <
        /div>
    );
};

export default FederalDashboard;
